@startuml
title Arquitectura MVP - PipelinePredict IA

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

rectangle "GitHub Actions / Jenkins / GitLab CI" as cicd
rectangle "API Java Spring Boot\nCapa oficial de datos" as java

database "PostgreSQL\nDatos históricos" as db
rectangle "Python ML + FastAPI\nConsume SOLO API Java" as python
rectangle "Streamlit Dashboard" as streamlit

cicd --> java : datos CI/CD
java --> db : lee/escribe
java --> python : expone REST /api/ml/*
python --> java : guarda predicciones vía REST
python --> streamlit : predicciones / métricas
streamlit --> java : dashboard / historial
streamlit --> python : predicción en tiempo real

note right of python
Python NO se conecta directo a PostgreSQL.
No usa psycopg2 ni SQLAlchemy contra la BD.
end note

@enduml
